column16: Freddie Freeman flies out to left fielder Rich Thompson.

Ryan Sweeney flies out to left fielder Matt Joyce.
Kelly Shoppach pops out to shortstop Elliot Johnson on the infield fly rule.
Mike Aviles singles on a ground ball to right fielder Ben Zobrist.    David Ortiz to 3rd.    Darnell McDonald to 2nd.
Cody Ross out on a sacrifice fly to center fielder Desmond Jennings.    Kevin Youkilis scores.
David Ortiz doubles (3) on a line drive to left fielder Matt Joyce.    Adrian Gonzalez scores.    Kevin Youkilis to 3rd.
Kevin Youkilis singles on a ground ball to center fielder Desmond Jennings.    Ryan Sweeney scores.    Dustin Pedroia scores.    Adrian Gonzalez to 2nd.
Adrian Gonzalez singles on a fly ball to left fielder Matt Joyce.    Ryan Sweeney to 3rd.    Dustin Pedroia to 2nd.
Dustin Pedroia singles on a ground ball to shortstop Elliot Johnson.

Raul Ibanez out on a sacrifice fly to center fielder Desmond Jennings.    Curtis Granderson scores.
